Authority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the province of
NEW BRUNSWICK for the implementation of NATIONAL SAFETY CODE STANDARD
NO. 14 (COMPLIANCE REVIEW - SAFETY RATING), a standard that ascribes a
